"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Norbactin Eye Drops (BF, BJ, CI, ET, GH, GM, GN, IN, KE, LR, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, NE, NG, SC, SD, SL, SN, TN, TZ, UG, ZM, ZW);",
"     </li>",
